text: Andrew Ratcliffe (3 May 1891 - 31 August 1974) was an Australian cricketer. He played 43 first-class matches for New South Wales between 1913/14 and 1928/29. ==See also== * List of New South Wales representative cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1891 births Category:1974 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:New South Wales cricketers Category:Cricketers from Sydney
